<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1216</hymn_number>
<title>yé hé huá běn wèi dà 迦南1216</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé hé huá běn wèi dà, běn wèi dà, wǒ men yào zàn měi tā, zàn měi tā.
 tā de míng chāo hū wàn shén zhī shàng, wǒ men dāng gāo shēng xuān yáng.
 rì guāng yuè guāng xīng guāng, shì tā bǎi shè zài tiān shàng.
 dòng wù zhí wù wàn wù, shì tā ān zhì zài de shàng.
 ràng niǎo ér zài tiān kōng fēi xiáng, ràng yú ér yóu zài hǎi yáng.
 yòng chén tǔ zào le wǒ men de mó yàng, shì àn zhào shén de xíng xiàng.
 gē chàng zhǔ de cí ài wú jiāng, chuàng zào tiān de gěi wǒ men gōng yǎng.
 yòu cì gěi wǒ men yǒng shēng hé pàn wàng, hái yǒu yī gè měi lì de jiā xiāng.</lyrics>
</song>